    "description": "ISB Corporation engages in the provision of embedded software development services for mobile, medical, and automotive applications in Japan. The company is involved in software development services; medical information systems, hospital system and medical device development; development of public systems for local governments and government agencies; business system development; integrates hardware and software to provide optimal embedded solutions. It also provides financial systems; infrastructure construction and operation design and maintenance services for cloud services; system operation services; and data center housing and hosting, as well as Al solutions. In addition, the company offers IT services, including system development, application development, and operation and maintenance; financial system and mobile system development; and consulting services. Further, it sells equipment associated with system and software development; and develops and sells access control systems and electric locks. ISB Corporation was incorporated in 1970 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
